\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces The \texttt  {.areal} binary format layout. A 256-byte header contains the ``REAL'' magic, version, flags, and incarnation ID. The section table indexes 9~section types, each with per-section BLAKE3 checksums. A 64-byte footer with ``REALEND\textbackslash 0'' magic provides format validation. LZ4 compression is optionally applied to section payloads.}}{4}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:format}{{3}{4}{The \texttt {.areal} binary format layout. A 256-byte header contains the ``REAL'' magic, version, flags, and incarnation ID. The section table indexes 9~section types, each with per-section BLAKE3 checksums. A 64-byte footer with ``REALEND\textbackslash 0'' magic provides format validation. LZ4 compression is optionally applied to section payloads}{figure.caption.5}{}}
